 <h1 class="title topictitle1">Thesaurus Navigator</h1>

 <div class="body conbody">
  <p class="p">The "Thesaurus Navigator" is located on the left of your work space in Thesaurus view. It
   includes key words that you can apply to the texts and objects metadata (passport data). </p>

  <p class="p">The toolbar of the "Thesaurus navigator" contains the following entries: </p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_jgp_qwb_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/thss_add.png"></img> Add Thesaurus Root
   Entry</p>

  <p class="p">This adds a new "Thesaurus Root" entry after the letter "P".</p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_vmg_hwb_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/ths-add.png"></img> Add Thesaurus Child
   Entry</p>

  <p class="p">This adds a new child entry to a selected root entry or child entry.</p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_ffn_kxb_qr" src="Images/icons/full/obj16/delete.png"></img> This moves an entry
   from the Thesaurus to <img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_dtn_nxb_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/bin.png"></img>
   Bin.</p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_zkc_1yb_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/search.png"></img> "Search": Search the
   Thesaurus for entries. </p>

  <p class="p"><strong class="ph b">Bin</strong></p>

  <p class="p">Entries deleted in "Thesaurus" appear in <img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_bz5_ny4_zr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/bin.png"></img> "Bin" tab. They are not grouped. Deleting an item here will remove it
   permanently. Please note that generating the list of the objects in the "Bin" tab may take up to
   one minute the first time you click it after installing BTS. After this the preview works faster. </p>

  <p class="p"><strong class="ph b">Drop-down menu</strong> "<img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_umy_spv_ps" src="Images/icons/extra%20icons/options_dreieck.png"></img>"</p>

  <p class="p">"Delete Permanenty": Delete selected entry completely.</p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_hk1_b1c_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/userrole.png"></img> "Edit
   Updaters/Readers": Assign user roles for thesaurus entries. </p>

  <p class="p"><img class="image" id="concept_art_dqd_4r__image_gq4_1bc_qr" src="Images/icons/full/icon16/history.png"></img> "Open Revision
   History": opens the history of the changes made for the selected
   lemma</p>

  
  <p class="p"></p>

  <p class="p">"Filter": Apply different filters on the thesaurus entires:</p>

  <p class="p">...by Project</p>

  <p class="p">...by Creator</p>

  <p class="p">...by Updaters</p>

  <p class="p">...by Review Status</p>

  <p class="p">...by Visibility</p>

  <p class="p">To apply the filter, activate the relevant checkboxes</p>

 </div>

